text: Rabin, the Last Day is a 2015 Israeli French political thriller movie directed by Amos Gitai and starring Tomer Sisley, Yitzhak Hiskiya, Michael Warshaviak, Einat Weizman, Yogev Yefet, Rotem Keinan, Tomer Russo, Uri Gottlieb, Gdalya Besser. ==Other websites== * Category:2015 thriller movies Category:Israeli movies Category:French thriller movies Category:Movies directed by Amos Gitai
